Package: plant
Title: A package for modelling forest trait ecology and evolution
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Richard G. FitzJohn and Daniel S. Falster
Maintainer: Richard G. FitzJohn <rich.fitzjohn@gmail.com>
Description: Solves trait, size and patch structured model
    from (Falster et al. 2010) using either method of
    characteristics or as stochastic, finite-sized population.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp, BH
Imports:
    Rcpp,
    R6,
    loggr,
    crayon,
    nleqslv,
    BB
Suggests:
    testthat,
    deSolve,
    numDeriv,
    parallel,
    RcppR6 (>= 0.2.3),
    knitr,
    plant.ml
VignetteBuilder: knitr
